<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>:) قَرَمُونَةُ،<span class="c5"> محرّكةً:</span> كُورَةٌ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>